OL,5, A community say they are in "disbelief"
OL,6, at plans to demolish a primary school  
OL,7, five years after it was abandoned due  
OL,8, to fears of a landslide.               
OL,10,FIn July 2019, Godre'r Graig Primary    
OL,11,FSchool near Pontardawe, Neath Port     
OL,12,FTalbot, was closed due to fears of a   
OL,13,Flandslide from an old quarry tip.      
OL,15,FPupils are are still being taught from 
OL,16,Ftemporary cabins three miles away.     
OL,18,FNeath Port Talbot council now plans to 
OL,19,Fbegin demolition on Friday, saying     
OL,20,Fother options had been "ruled out".    
